<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Receipt - VirdisPay</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .success-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #28a745;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .receipt-summary {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #28a745;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .merchant-info {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .details-table td {
            padding: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .details-table td:first-child {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #666;
            width: 40%;
        }
        .crypto-benefits {
            background: #d4edda;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .network-info {
            background: #fff3cd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .tx-hash {
            font-family: monospace;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .print-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #6c757d;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 10px 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üåø VirdisPay</div>
            <div class="success-icon">‚úÖ</div>
            <h1 style="color: #28a745; margin: 0;">Payment Successful!</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Thank you for your payment, {{customerName}}! Your transaction has been successfully processed and confirmed.</p>

            <div class="receipt-summary">
                <div class="amount">${{amount}} {{currency}}</div>
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #666;">Payment successfully processed</p>
            </div>

            <div class="merchant-info">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1976d2;">üè™ Merchant Information</h3>
                <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>{{merchantName}}</strong></p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #666;">Powered by VirdisPay</p>
            </div>

            <table class="details-table">
                <tr>
                    <td>Transaction ID:</td>
                    <td><strong>{{transactionId}}</strong></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Description:</td>
                    <td>{{description}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Payment Method:</td>
                    <td>Cryptocurrency ({{currency}})</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Network:</td>
                    <td>{{network}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Gas Fee:</td>
                    <td>${{gasFee}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Blockchain Hash:</td>
                    <td class="tx-hash">{{txHash}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Timestamp:</td>
                    <td>{{timestamp}}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <div class="crypto-benefits">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #155724;">üöÄ Why Crypto Payments?</h3>
                <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li><strong>Ultra-Low Fees:</strong> Only ${{gasFee}} transaction fee</li>
                    <li><strong>Instant Confirmation:</strong> No waiting for bank processing</li>
                    <li><strong>Global Access:</strong> Works anywhere in the world</li>
                    <li><strong>Secure:</strong> Blockchain technology ensures security</li>
                    <li><strong>Private:</strong> Your payment data is protected</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="network-info">
                <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #856404;">üåê Network Information</h4>
                <p style="margin: 0;">This payment was processed on the <strong>{{network}}</strong> network, providing ultra-low fees and fast confirmation times. The transaction is now permanently recorded on the blockchain.</p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>What's Next?</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Your payment has been confirmed on the blockchain</li>
                <li>The merchant has been notified of your payment</li>
                <li>You should receive your order confirmation shortly</li>
                <li>Keep this receipt for your records</li>
            </ul>

            {{#if merchantContact}}
            <p><strong>Questions about your order?</strong> Contact the merchant at <a href="mailto:{{merchantContact}}">{{merchantContact}}</a></p>
            {{/if}}

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <button onclick="window.print()" class="print-button">üñ®Ô∏è Print Receipt</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>VirdisPay</strong> - Professional Crypto Payments for Cannabis Industry</p>
            <p>¬© {{currentYear}} VirdisPay. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>



